{"tid":922594,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"日本政府掛海賊旗[sosad]","createTime":"2018-11-30T13:38:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-05T08:20:49.000Z","uid":66943,"like":27,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"65c8455471c29bb375bced8dde994b09e26bb0aa","tid":922594,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T13:38:32.000Z","msg":"海賊王漫畫作者尾田榮一郎的故鄉熊本縣要斥資1300萬日元建造路飛銅像，現在這個路飛銅像終於落成。今天（11月30日），路飛銅像揭幕典禮在熊本召開，參加的人員都帶著路飛的草帽出席，場面非常令人感動。熊本縣政府廳還升起了草帽團的海賊旗，真是非常厲害了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QNt9S1u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQNt9S1u.jpg&h=5363ba14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cMd9S1w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcMd9S1w.png&h=97b1b45c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g6D9S1s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg6D9S1s.jpg&h=32c6257c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jgxntzN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjgxntzN.jpg&h=fe08cb2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iAvXhs6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiAvXhs6.jpg&h=56987584&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ABb6mt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ABb6mt.jpg&h=2eebdb5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/riRSQN8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FriRSQN8.jpg&h=f06b111b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d9a66cf4165a723e983d87af9cea7c4b4707c076","tid":922594,"uid":45629,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T13:52:22.000Z","msg":"隻熊本熊好搞笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54b8cc8f91a266c10c788fd058c3325eef8dc567","tid":922594,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-3